15 (a) A person engages in retaliation if the person treats another individual less favorably because
16 the individual made a good-faith [complaint] report about conduct prohibited by this rule or partic-
17 ipated in an investigation about conduct that is prohibited by this rule.
18 (b) A person engages in retaliation if the person treats another individual less favorably because
