1 (B) [A nonpartisan staff] An appointing authority who receives the investigator’s final report
2 under subparagraph (A)(i) of this paragraph, or the Legislative Administrator upon receiving the
3 [investigator’s] final investigative report under subparagraph [(A)(iii) or (iv)] (A)(ii) or (iii) of this
4 paragraph, shall determine remedial measures described in subsection (15) of this rule within 14 days
